# nested-prefix-sibling-blocks

## Input

```
s {
  a {
    x 1
  }
  b {
    y 2
  }
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..42
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..42
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@6..22
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "a"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@8..9 "{"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
      SPACE@10..14 "    "
      ENTRY@14..18
        WORD_KEY@14..15
          WORD@14..15 "x"
        SPACE@15..16 " "
        INTEGER@16..17
          NUMERAL@16..17 "1"
        NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
      SPACE@18..20 "  "
      CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}"
      NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
    SPACE@22..24 "  "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@24..40
      WORD_KEY@24..25
        WORD@24..25 "b"
      SPACE@25..26 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@26..27 "{"
      NEWLINE@27..28 "\n"
      SPACE@28..32 "    "
      ENTRY@32..36
        WORD_KEY@32..33
          WORD@32..33 "y"
        SPACE@33..34 " "
        INTEGER@34..35
          NUMERAL@34..35 "2"
        NEWLINE@35..36 "\n"
      SPACE@36..38 "  "
      CLOSE_BRACE@38..39 "}"
      NEWLINE@39..40 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@40..41 "}"
    NEWLINE@41..42 "\n"
```

